Requires Mono 2.10 - .NET 4.0 Framework to run.

Dll References are in Binrefs.
the linux lib's are from Ubuntu 10.10 - libSDL and libIL(DevIL);

Installation Notes.

Compile using VS2010.
Copy the files from binrefs that associate to your operating system to your Build Directory.

All data is stored in data folder in the same directory.
